    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、何を見てるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you looking at‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？　な、渚か……いや、これは、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! Oh‚ Nagisa… well‚ er…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n月ストメンバーの今月のスケジュール、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's—\nIs that Moon Tempest’s schedule for this month?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ。見られてしまったらもうしょうがないな\nざっとでいいから、目を通してくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ no point hiding it now that you saw it already.\nHere‚ take a look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3333333999994,
          "startTime": 30.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ\n琴乃ちゃんは女性誌での撮影が多いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ okay.\nKotono-chan has a lot of photo sessions with women’s magazines.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはクールでかっこいいもんなぁ……\n同世代の女の子が憧れそうですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It fits well with Kotono-chan's image of coolness.\nGirls around her age look up to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんはお仕事の種類が豊富なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like Saki-chan is doing a lot of different work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "この間はミュージカルでしたけど\n最近はナレーションにレポーターまで……凄いな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was in that musical‚\nbut now she’s doing narration and even reporting… Wow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんは慣れないお仕事でも入念に準備をして\n丁寧にこなせるのが凄いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when the work is unfamiliar‚\nSaki-chan makes proper preparations and gets the job done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんは\nどうしてこれを私に……はっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why are you showing\nthis to me‚ {user}-san… Oh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}